Use the standard library
This is how to remove_duplicates of numbers:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that count is 0
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this n times:
         When item j in numbers is x, then:
            Increase count
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      When count is 1, then:
         Add result to x
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know